// For now, it's a static placeholder.
---

<div id="manuscript-container">
    <div id="manuscript-content">
        <h1>The Ramayana</h1>
        <p>In the ancient city of Ayodhya, ruled by the righteous King Dasharatha, a divine prince was born. He was Rama, an incarnation of Vishnu, destined to walk the earth and establish dharma...</p>
        <p>His story is one of courage, devotion, and the eternal struggle between good and evil, a timeless epic that has guided generations.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    #manuscript-container {
        /* This container is a flexbox to center the content perfectly */
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: 100; /* Must be on top of the papyrus overlay */
        pointer-events: none; /* So it doesn't block clicks initially */
    }

    #manuscript-content {
        color: #1a1a1a; /* High-contrast, near-black text */
        font-family: Georgia, serif; /* A classic, readable serif font */
        max-width: 650px; /* Set a max width for readability */
        line-height: 1.8;
        text-align: center;

        /* Initial state for our placeholder animation (invisible and slightly moved down) */
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
    }

    #manuscript-content h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    #manuscript-content p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
</style>